quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,"Alif, Lam, Mim."
  2,2,"Esho nishio Eshitabu shibulamwo obukanakani bwosibwosi, nishiobulunjifu khubalia abaria Nyasaye."
  2,3,"Balia abasuubilanga mufilalolekha, abaswaliyanga (iswala) khatsotso, ne barusinjia eshihanwa okhurula mumukabo kwa khubakabile."
  2,4,"Balia abasuubilanga khu kalia keshibwa khwiwe, nende kalia keshibwa imbeli wuwo, ne basuubilanga muno obulamu bwomwikulu."
  2,5,"Abo bali khubulunjifu okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, ne abo nibo balibura."